      "content": "thanks. i already drank some water but i still feel really out of it and my speech is still all jumbled. do i really need a doctor for this? i dont want to spend all my money on an ER visit in a foreign country if it's just the heat. can i just sleep it off with some ibuprofen and more Gatorade?",
